snippet.title: Paint the Town Red (Greenlight Trailer)
snippet.description:
The Steam Greenlight & 7DFPS trailer for Paint the Town Red

This version was made in 7 days for the #7DFPS game jam. Please visit our Steam Greenlight page to help us build a full version.

Vote for us on Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=341471927


Music: "Dead Drop" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
